      <div resp="part:emfr" type="translation">
        <p n="1">Prosperity! Fortune!</p>
        <p n="1-2"><unclear>Second</unclear> year of the glorious Vayiramēkavarman<note>That is, Sanskrit Vajrameghavarman.</note>.</p>
        <p n="2-3">We, the members of the assembly <supplied reason="subaudible">of</supplied> Poykainallūr in the Tāmaṟkōṭṭam.</p>
        <p n="4-6">For the Mahādeva, Lord of the glorious Tiruvakaṭtīśvaram <supplied reason="subaudible">of</supplied> this village <gap reason="undefined"></gap> permanent food offerings <gap reason="undefined"></gap> that <gap reason="undefined"></gap> has given as glorious food offerings <gap reason="undefined"></gap></p>
